<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="47" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,152,1098]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,343,1031,1057]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">Etymology:</emphasis>
This species is named in honour of Kristian Fauchald as a tribute of his major contribution to polychaete systematics, his kindness and long friendship with us, and facilitating our visit the CBC.
</paragraph>
